              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "Let's solve the equation:\n\n\\[\n\\sin(x) + x^2 = 42\n\\]\n\nThis is a transcendental equation (involves both trigonometric and algebraic terms), so we need to use a numerical method to find solutions. Let's find all real solutions.",
